      "rationale": "Testing followed ASTM F1717 at a single load rate (5 mm/min) and single temperature condition. The required level of 3 demands multiple test conditions or load rates; only one condition was evaluated, yielding an achieved level of 2. This shortfall is documented as a known gap."
